---
title: Kiwi Chicken & Roast Kumara Dijon Salad with Avocado & Parmesan
description: Juicy, pan-fried chicken thigh is the perfect vehicle to let our Kiwi spice blend shine, imparting it’s delicious smokey flavours! And when you add roasted kumara and pile it all onto crisp lettuce with charred corn and creamy avo, you get a plate full of goodness!

